  "Description": {
    "English": "A bundle of upgrades compatible with all <span class=\"name name-stellar\">person Multi-Tools</span>.<br><br>Includes a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Multi-Tool Expansion Slot</span>, which may be wired into a Multi-Tool at a Space Station <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool Upgrade Rack</span>, as well as a unique <span class=\"name name-technology\">Upgrade Module</span>, which can be immediately installed by hand to enhance an existing Multi-Tool technology.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "与所有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">个人多用途工具</span>兼容的升级部件包。<br><br>内附一个<span class=\"name name-technology\">多用途工具扩展栏位</span>，可在空间站<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具升级架</span>将其装到选中的多用途工具上。除此以外该部件包还含有一项独特<span class=\"name name-technology\">升级模块</span>，能够随时手动安装并强化一种现有的多用途工具技术。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一組與所有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">個人工具組</span>相容的同捆升級。<br><br>包括可在太空站<span class=\"name name-stellar\">工具組升級架</span>接上工具組的<span class=\"name name-technology\">工具組擴充欄位</span>，和一個能立即透過手動安裝來強化目前工具組科技的獨特<span class=\"name name-technology\">升級模組</span>。"
  },
